{"about_the_game":"I am a <strong>solo dev </strong>that have been making games with passion for years, I hope you will enjoy Hoverflow, <strong>my first big project</strong> \ud83d\udda4<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/SurfTitle.png?t=1731602058\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/Surf.gif?t=1731602058\" /><br>Inspired from the famous mod from Counter Strike, surf on all kinds of ramps ! <strong>Intuitive tutorials</strong> will help you learn and master this <strong>unique mechanic</strong> and <strong>cool audio design</strong> makes it even more fun !<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/HopTitle.png?t=1731602058\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/Hop.gif?t=1731602058\" /><br><strong>Jump</strong>, <strong>double jump</strong>, and <strong>even bunny hops</strong> if you have enough speed ! Use them all and chose wisely your timing to <strong>keep your flow</strong> !<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/ExploreTitle.png?t=1731602058\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/Explore.gif?t=1731602058\" /><br>Take the time to enjoy beautiful watercolor textures and a <strong>mysterious atmosphere</strong> alongside a peaceful <strong>35 minutes long soundtrack</strong>. Don't forget to explore the world to <strong>uncover secrets</strong>... be careful though, some might try to escape ! <strong>Hidden characters</strong> might reveal a thing or two about the world you live in as well...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/TimeTrialsTitle.png?t=1731602058\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/Medals.gif?t=1731602058\" /><br>Beat quickly the <strong>30+ handcrafted levels</strong> to earn medals from <strong>Bronze to Gold</strong>... or even <strong>try to beat my time</strong> if you have what it takes ! Compare your times with your friends on <strong>leaderboards </strong>as well !<br><br>Join the Discord if you have any question, I usually answer pretty quickly !<br>Simon.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Smile for the speedcam !","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1280060/16e51dab2ae6fe398a5133aeed6180a403c9e1ce.jpg"},{"name":"Gold member","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1280060/dc0af6b9665cbe38a6f2792a4a4800d799d8d5bb.jpg"},{"name":"Mike Horn","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1280060/888f12d96a433b19e714b8582a4a137b73b0a1bd.jpg"},{"name":"Good morning Mr. Kent","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1280060/c25d8f33b28248e289a09a293b660241da50a462.jpg"},{"name":"Crippled","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1280060/1153d9372b254b0abd68764ef8ac41516524ab34.jpg"},{"name":"Bunny Rabbit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1280060/b8a072ca8a3bab7389e40194c206b7cd00b9cf1d.jpg"},{"name":"School starts in 30 minutes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1280060/5c761d60f93444cfb9d5a7a380180dbd755da894.jpg"},{"name":"To infinity and beyond","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1280060/d9aed91a35bf62af642c68dc28ea8e94772cc28d.jpg"}],"total":8},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731